    <body>The Medium drop-down shows all the medium styles that are in effect in the editor. For example, if the mobile layout is displayed, both the mobile and tablet medium styles apply and are selected. If (multiple) is displayed in the Medium drop-down, that is  indication that multiple styles are applied. Content in the editor is rendered with all applicable styles (according to the width).</body>
</html>